09:54.840 --> 09:55.600
Mu Qingyun.

09:56.000 --> 09:58.120
Awak sekarang semakin berpendirian sendiri ya.

09:58.120 --> 09:58.960
Kawan saya,

09:59.240 --> 10:00.040
